  "primary_issue": "SQL injection vulnerability due to unsanitized user input concatenated directly into SQL query.",
  "evidence": "String sql = \"select * from t_user where name='\" + name + \"' and pass='\" + pass + \"'\";",
  "fix_summary": "Use parameterized queries (PreparedStatement) instead of string concatenation to safely handle user input."
